夢冇發現<br />\n好自然咁拎住袋垃圾等𨋢入𨋢仲要一路撳電話<br />\n旁若無人咁撚樣<br />\n直至落到大堂個看更想幫我開門嘅時候用十分奇怪嘅眼神望住我...<br />\n先發現瀨撚咗嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即刻面懵懵咁衝返上去<br />\n好在呀姐未上到嚟倒垃圾同冇人執咗去<br />\n同埋來回同𨋢都冇撞到其他住客<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c832abb90389ba847b0951b3f57ff251d4ecfcd6","tid":1155061,"uid":230890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T00:35:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f13635d47494b8822907422a46289d446092712","tid":1155061,"uid":4052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T00:48:52.000Z","msg":"試過朝早返工掉垃圾去後樓梯個垃圾桶既時候連埋部電話一齊掉咗，返到公司都唔發覺，以為係自己唔記得帶電話。去到5點幾果陣突然諗起可能掉垃圾掉埋，即刻打返屋企叫老母幫我去垃圾桶揾吓，竟然揾得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好彩下晝無人倒垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dff19d1fba8bafb3f89bbcc7e9f553e3af3bf05","tid":1155061,"uid":6285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13610fad0e9a5081f325808f4afecf98926bfdf3","tid":1155061,"uid":69775,"like":125,"dislike":3,"score":122,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T17:13:46.000Z","msg":"渣住張包紙 dum左個包 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T00:52:12.000Z","msg":"我係食雪糕 想dum張紙 最後dum咗雪糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c4b47c0f3a63f25a636b29db12b7bc0695c8fa","tid":1155061,"uid":6285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T00:55:10.000Z","msg":"除咗條鑽石鍊喺枱面 之後又呻到成枱鼻涕紙<br />\n一嘢掃晒去dum<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56bf55ae2b902c888ab3fbc5ffb8e0174f2dce5","tid":1155061,"uid":77855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:00:16.000Z","ms